PrecisApprove the appointment by the Minister of Transport of MICHAEL WILLIAM FURLONG, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Edward Frank Anthony, who has resigned.
